{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Live Streaming and Gameplay Welcome!!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>**[Calligraphy Simulator Game]**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Write characters on Japanese calligraphy paper using a brush. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the art of calligraphy on your computer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully reproduce the brush techniques like *tome*, *hane*, and *harai*!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304490/extras/traler_steam_gif.gif?t=1731578220\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">**[Hiragana &amp; Katakana]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn how to write hiragana and katakana by tracing the 50-syllable charts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">**[Calligraphy Practice]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Practice calligraphy following examples and get used to brush movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are various examples, including single characters, two characters, four-character idioms, and large-format paper.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">**[Sutra Copying]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Handwrite the *Heart Sutra* and engrave its sacred words into your heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It could also be used as a form of atonement, like waterfall meditation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">**[Kanji Test]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test yourself on the kanji learned in elementary school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Self-score and check whether you got them right!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">**[Free Mode]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In different settings, feel free to write anything with a brush.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Play!The Japanese Calligraphy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3304490/696f99f21c1aae24086fb75c0a4324475a92b687.jpg"},{"name":"Hiragana Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pub